 East London - An intelligence-driven operation was conducted by members of East London Crime Intelligent with the assistance of East London POPS and Mdantsane flying squad at Beacon Bay on Thursday. "A 28-year-old female suspect was arrested for Dealing in Drugs alternative charge Possession of Drugs as per Beacon Bay case weight 20kg of dagga with a street value of R15 000," said police spokesperson, Captain Hazel Mqala. She would appear in the East London Magistrate's Court on Thursday. Follow more RNEWS articles, subscribe to our YouTube channel and for breaking news LIKE us on Facebook. For news on the Western Cape click here. For great savings on life’s little pleasures visit Bargain Buys!  Know somebody who is getting married, Wedding and Function can assist.  Have kids, then you need to visit Kids Connection. Enjoy food and travel, then visit Home Food and Travel. Need assistance with an online presence, visit Agency One. 